Introduction

Fong Atilla is a Hongkongese-Australian trainee.

Atilla participated in the survival show “Asia Super Young” in 2023, where he was eliminated in episode 14, ranking 19th. In 2024, he joined JTBC’s survival show “PROJECT 7” but was eliminated in episode 11 after ranking 24th place.
